                {
                    "title": "<span style=\"font-size:26px;\">&nbsp;</span>",
                    "content": "<div class=\"references\">\n<h1>Sources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Demographic and health surveys (DHS)</li>\n<li>Multiple indicator cluster surveys (MICS)</li>\n<li>United Nations Children\u2019s Fund (UNICEF)</li>\n<li>National surveys</li>\n<li>World Bank</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Related stories and further reading</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a class=\"narrative-ref\" href=\"https://worlds-women-2020-data-undesa.hub.arcgis.com/app/50dd1b2d6167437693178836261522e6#NV1\" target=\"_blank\">Intimate partner physical and/or sexual violence</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",
